descriptionHtml:
First off, this is a simple texture, doesn\'t add any food (yet?)

This changes the cooking pot\'s stew texture. I always thought it looked like vomit, and since I have a hunger mod and a cooking mod, I use the pot o\' stew a lot. Got sick of it, made a new texture.

Also has a normal map, adds some texture to it ;)

Update- Added NMM download, as far as I know, it should work just fine.
author: Hooker Heels
